      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a champ. It\u2019s in great shape and has been super well-loved\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks sharp on the road. It runs beautifully and is totally ready for its next big adventure with a new owner! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin. You\u2019re going to love how it drives!",
      "price": 34500.0,
