    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that provides a broad, linear powerband up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a functional M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing inspection. The chassis maintains excellent lateral rigidity with its MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. While the finish shows light stone chipping and minor interior bolster wear typical of a driven enthusiast vehicle, the powertrain and drivetrain remain in peak operational condition.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
