      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful ownership. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin where the premium upholstery and all technological features\u2014including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control\u2014remain in excellent working order. Mechanically, the car is turn-key ready; it shifts smoothly, accelerates with ease, and has a documented history of timely oil changes and preventative maintenance. Having recently passed a full multi-point inspection and featuring tires with significant tread remaining, this car offers the peace of mind of a much newer model. It is a reliable, eye-catching driver that has been genuinely cared for.",
      "price": 36500.0,
